                <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> Valerius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">C</supplied>la</abbr><ex>udia</ex></expan> Alpinus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">G</supplied>lanat</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">l</supplied>eg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> X <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>tus</ex></expan> Albius <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>agent</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>cura</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> Coelio <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>secundo</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>erede</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeile 1-4 A mit deutlicher Überlänge der rechten Schräghaste. Zeile 7: Ursprünglich eingemeißeltes CVRA zu H P korrigiert, C und V noch deutlich zu erkennen, A schwach. Zeile 9 lässt sich als Secundo h(erede) oder secundo h(erede) (Ersatzerbe) lesen. (B): Z. 3: Hild; Vorbeck; Mosser: Glanat(ia); Z. 7: AE 1958; AE 1960: H V P; Lamboglia: v(ivens) p(osuit); Krüger; Vorbeck; Mosser: v p(osuit). Nach Mosser besaß der Soldat kein cognomen, Alpinus wäre also als weitere Herkunftsangabe zu verstehen.</p>
            </div>
